    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = tmp
    tmp = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.52 - v1 + 0.06)) * wp.sin((v1 + 0.47 - v2 + 0.31)))
    tmp = ((wp.sin(v1 + 0.64) + wp.abs(v2 + 0.94)) * ((tmp + 0.55 * v1 + 0.62) + (v2 + 0.86 - v0 + 0.82)))
    v0 = wp.cos(0.75)
    v1 = (0.77 + wp.abs(v1))
    data[tid] = v0
